  "description": "High sync in a vast empty space. Drama=0.9 locks partials into crystalline purity while Stage=0.85 places the sound at infinite distance. The result is a single point of harmonic light in an immense darkness — beautiful, isolated, unreachable. The longer you listen, the more detail emerges from the void.",
